  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel's restaurant is bright and airy, spilling out onto the terrace that overlooks the harbour and lake. A varied buffet breakfast includes hot and cold options from freshly baked pastries and cold cuts and cheeses to eggs made to order. Dinner is three courses with a choice and once a week in high season the hotel hold a gala dinner with a special menu. </p>
<p>A pizzeria is open during high season and offers a casual dining option for lunch (payable locally). Evenings can be spent enjoying local drinks in the bar, where live music is performed once a week (from approx. 17 May - 30 Sep). The bar is also open to the public.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
