  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). </p>
<p><strong>Standard Balcony Rooms </strong>have a small balcony with table and chairs.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms</strong> have fantastic views across Lake Garda.</p>
<p><strong>Lake View Rooms with Balcony </strong>have a balcony that you can sit out on and enjoy the stunning lake views. </p>
<p><strong>Standard Rooms for sole use</strong> are also available.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning (June to mid-September)</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Mini-fridge</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request.</p>
<p><strong>General Information</strong></p>
<p>The hotel is made up of two buildings of the same quality and standard, both connected by an internal corridor. Rooms can be located in either building. </p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €2.50 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
